values: Here are Thatcher's 3 month pictures. I just got around to scanning them onto the computer, even though today is his 4-month birthday! He had these taken on September 9th. Hope everyone has a great week!
Here are some pics of my little guy.....he will be 4 months on the 9th!
Thatcher and his daddy dressed alike! Thatcher and his 18 mo old cousin, Sydney Thatcher and all his friends!
Newborn Hospital Pics If you go to this website and click on "Thatcher Hayden" then it will prompt you for an ID, which is 76311468, and you can see his newborn hospital pic.

My son was born on 6/9/06, 1 day before his due date, at 6:28 pm. He was 6 lbs 5 oz and 19.25 inches long. We named him Thatcher Hayden and he is adorable. I will probably write up my birth story next week, I am trying to get in the last little bit of daddy time before he goes back to work Monday. I will post it as soon as I finish.

I cannot believe I only have a few weeks left! And at my OB appt. yesterday they said I was measuring 8 days ahead, so it could possibly be sooner. I am not holding my breath that it will be, but I am just amazed how soon I could have a baby!
I am no good at this posting pics things, and I have tried NUMEROUS times to do a stupid cut but nothing works for me. I am computer-stupid!
